dct_description_sm: Depths shown by soundings and isolines; relief by hachures and spot heights.
Includes 4 inset charts, Tidal Information table.
Shows coasts, shoals, islands, drainage, vegetation.
Map text in English; otherwise in Japanese.
Descriptive text, such as "Chain of Lakes."
Japan Hydrographic Department seal in upper left margin.
Extra small correction date made in green ink, illegible.
